Set up local server:
brew cask install ngrok 
ngrok http 5000 
web will be specified on terminal

How to setup Flask:
pip install Flask
export FLASK_ENV=development (sets up debugger so that local changes are updated in run immediately)
FLASK_APP=app.py 
flask run

Where to find the web?
http://127.0.0.1:5000/chatbot

How to test it on terminal?
curl localhost:5000/chatbot -d '{"goal":"sleep"}' -H 'Content-Type: application/json'
